  "text": "Previously features and descriptors have been extensively evaluated on planar and parallax-free scenes [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . We have tested the two methods on the scenes available at [17], using a program, also downloaded at [17] , to verify correspondences. We have used an overlap error threshold of 50% throughout.",
